    suit an interactive editor.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION

   	tar zxvf <dist_file>.tar.gz 
   	cd <dist_directory>
   	perl Build.PL
	./Build test

If you want to install this software without packaging, type also:

        ./Build install
